csdl.jupiter.model.reviewissue
Class KeyManager

java.lang.Object
  csdl.jupiter.model.reviewissue.KeyManager
Direct Known Subclasses:
ResolutionKeyManager, SeverityKeyManager, StatusKeyManager, TypeKeyManager
public abstract class KeyManager
extends java.lang.Object

Provides the order (priority) of an item. The main purpose is to search the index of a certain keys type of the item.

add

public void add(java.lang.String key,

Adds the key and its value of an item. Ignore the second keys if the keys already exist in the manager (i.e No duplication for the keys). Sets empty string if key or/and its value is null.

Parameters:
key - the keys to add in the manager.
